OL,3,C'Exceptional wet weather' sinks farmer
OL,4,Cconfidence to all-time low
OL,6,FFarmer confidence in England and Wales
OL,7,Fhas collapsed to an all-time low, with
OL,8,Fmore than four-fifths saying they have
OL,9,Fbeen negatively affected by months of
OL,10,Fwet weather, sector leaders have
OL,11,Fwarned.
OL,13,FAll areas of farming - arable,
OL,14,Flivestock, poultry, horticulture and
OL,15,Fdairy - expect to decrease production
OL,16,Fover the next year, a poll by the
OL,17,FNational Farmers Union (NFU) found.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/15
