OL,3,C'Exceptional wet weather' sinks farmer
OL,4,Cconfidence to all-time low
OL,6,FAlmost 800 farmer and grower members
OL,7,Fwere surveyed between November 21 and
OL,8,FJanuary 5 about the challenges they
OL,9,Fare facing and their expectations for
OL,10,Fthe year ahead.
OL,12,FThe results published on Monday showed
OL,13,Fboth short and mid-term confidence -
OL,14,Ffarmers' outlook on the next year and
OL,15,Fnext three years - to be at their
OL,16,Flowest levels since the annual
OL,17,Fresearch began in 2010.
OL,19,FArable and livestock farmers were
OL,20,Ffound to be particularly pessimistic
OL,21,Ftowards both.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/15
