OL,6,F"I don't think anyone can
OL,7,Funderestimate the impact that this
OL,8,Flast 18 months of exceptional weather
OL,9,Fhas had," he said.
OL,11,FThe conditions have compounded other
OL,12,Fproblems for English and Welsh
OL,13,Ffarmers, such as increased costs,
OL,14,Finflationary pressures, labour
OL,15,Fshortages and cheaper imports, he said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/15
