OL,6,FResults of the survey suggest that the
OL,7,Fhighest proportion of farmers see the
OL,8,Fphase-out of the old European Union
OL,9,F(EU) Basic Payment Scheme towards new
OL,10,Fsubsidy schemes as an issue that will
OL,11,Fnegatively impact their businesses in
OL,12,F2024.
OL,14,FClosely following in second was the
OL,15,Fissue of high input costs - like fuel
OL,16,Fand fertiliser, which ranked highest
OL,17,Fin last year's survey.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/15
