OL,4,Cconfidence to all-time low
OL,6,FThe NFU warned that ultimately many
OL,7,Ffarm businesses are at risk this year,
OL,8,Fciting Office for National Statistics
OL,9,F(ONS) figures that more than 8,000
OL,10,Ffarms have been lost between 2019 and
OL,11,F2023.
OL,13,FIts survey found that 65% of farmers
OL,14,Fsaid their profits are declining or
OL,15,Ftheir business may not survive,
OL,16,Fcompared to 50% last year.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/15
