OL,6,F"Confidence has collapsed after months
OL,7,Fof devastating flooding, unsustainably
OL,8,Fhigh production costs and low market
OL,9,Freturns, and against a backdrop of
OL,10,Freduced farm support as we transition
OL,11,Fto a new Domestic Agriculture Policy
OL,12,Fand associated farm support," Mr
OL,13,FBradshaw said.
OL,15,F"Any business owner knows that without
OL,16,Fconfidence and a steady cash flow,
OL,17,Fthat business will struggle to re-
OL,18,Finvest and remain viable."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/15
