OL,6,FExperts have recently warned that
OL,7,Flower yields from key crops could lead
OL,8,Fto higher food prices if the losses
OL,9,Fcannot be offset by imports from a
OL,10,Fstronger global commodities market.
OL,12,FBut Mr Bradshaw argued that relying on
OL,13,Fimports is "naive at best and foolish
OL,14,Fat worst" as climate change grows as a
OL,15,Frisk to food systems globally.
OL,17,F"Britain cannot afford to lose its
OL,18,Fability to feed itself," he said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/15
