OL,6,FIn its general election manifesto, the
OL,7,Funion outlined solutions for political
OL,8,Fparties to adopt to tackle the
OL,9,Fbreakdown in farmer confidence and
OL,10,Fsafeguard homegrown food production.
OL,12,FThese include rewarding farmers fairly
OL,13,Ffor their role in mitigating flood
OL,14,Frisk, transitioning smoothly to new
OL,15,Fenvironmental schemes that are open to
OL,16,Fall farmers and ensuring profitable
OL,17,Flong-term, food-producing businesses.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/15
