OL,6,FThe union is also calling on
OL,7,Fpoliticians to establish minimum
OL,8,Fstandards to promote fair and
OL,9,Ffunctioning supply chains and
OL,10,Festablish core production standards
OL,11,Fthat apply to agri-food imports.
OL,13,FMr Bradshaw said: "Farmers are
OL,14,Fcarrying the risk within the supply
OL,15,Fchain and with the huge volatility
OL,16,Fwe've seen in the input markets and in
OL,17,Foutput prices in recent years.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G11/15
