OL,6,F"That risk is just getting too high
OL,7,Ffor many businesses to take and we now
OL,8,Fneed some solid foundations put in
OL,9,Fplace that are going to underpin our
OL,10,Ffood production for the future."
OL,12,FAsked about voting sentiment among his
OL,13,Fmembers, he said the rural vote is
OL,14,F"still very much up for grabs", adding
OL,15,Fthat the demographic is looking for
OL,16,Fpolicies that are going to underpin
OL,17,Fprofitable food production.
