OL,6,FFarming minister Mark Spencer said: "I
OL,7,Fpay tribute to all our farmers and
OL,8,Ftheir hard work to put food on our
OL,9,Ftables, day in day out.
OL,11,F"Backing British farmers remains at
OL,12,Fthe heart of this government's
OL,13,Fapproach, from maintaining the #2.4
OL,14,Fbillion annual budget, ensuring
OL,15,Ffairness in our supply chains and
OL,16,Flaunching the largest ever grant offer
OL,17,Ffor farmers in 2024.
