OL,6,F"Our farmers have faced one of the
OL,7,Fwettest periods on record in England,
OL,8,Fand I have seen first-hand the impact
OL,9,Fthis has had.
OL,11,F"The Farming Recovery Fund is offering
OL,12,Fsupport to farmers to help recover
OL,13,Ffrom uninsurable damage and we are
OL,14,Flooking at how we can expand the
OL,15,Fscheme and improve support for those
OL,16,Faffected.
OL,18,F"I will continue to listen and work
OL,19,Fwith farmers to look at what further
OL,20,Fsupport can be offered during this
OL,21,Fchallenging period."
